casebody.data:
Tom LUEY, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. March 3, 1928. Rehearing Denied March 28, 1928. No. 5035. John E. Jackson, of New Orleans, La., for appellant. E. E. Talbot, Asst. U. S. Atty., of New Orleans, La., for the United States.

Before WALKER, BRYAN, and FOSTER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The order or decree appealed from is affirmed.
